{"tid":2022594,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"新東人邊有可能唔選羅庭輝？","createTime":"2020-05-18T12:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T15:21:58.000Z","uid":12354,"like":24,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1dba15f97f182b97272f09940e9a8db792ffa231","tid":2022594,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGR4UBg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGR4UBg.png&h=1043818b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢其實睇得好通透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>1. 議會內勇武抗爭並不可取</ins></span><br />\n你喺立會勇武極咪又係衝上主席台，仲可以做到啲咩？唔係啲人唔夠勇武，而係你冇可能勇武到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇吓Big雲今日就知，佢可以為選票衝上主席台比你睇，最後咪又係會照開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>2. 35＋攬炒可能性微乎其微，入立會只為佢嘅資源同影響力</ins></span><br />\n有研究過都知，35＋係妙想天開嘅事，必須要諗未能夠達到35＋嘅Plan。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縱觀所有立會議員，冇一個人(郭榮鏗可能都算半個嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)係用緊佢嘅影響力做打國際線，反而得G鋒呢個冇任何公職嘅人做緊，咁啲資源不如比哂佢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年過去，好多嘢都唔同咗。要認清嘅一樣嘢係，街頭戰線已經好難打，國際戰線嘅重要性慢慢浮現出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一日突然睇到呢條片，發現呢位拉麵師傅對黃色經濟圈嘅睇法好通透，有興趣可以由7:58開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sOzlcH4f3mU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsOzlcH4f3mU&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=75d4b465\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sOzlcH4f3mU</a><br />\n//冇黃色經濟圈並唔係買贖罪劵，而係壯大自己嘅經濟體，先有Bragaining Power同政府議價。//<br />\n不過要記住嘅嘢係，唔好食黃店就當參與咗抗爭，真正要做嘅係將佢融入你嘅生活。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，係黃色經濟圈，唔係黃色飲食圈"},{"pid":"8d6f26b9df9f99d6fdc6ed333b32fe9a45b3734f","tid":2022594,"uid":267054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:07:19.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec183388cfab97f521f61aa749a35056306da7da","tid":2022594,"uid":267054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"啱啱經過街站拎咗佢份傳單嚟睇 政綱主打本土經濟 思路清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56434a2547b3540cc20366b9970c949047ca7a93","tid":2022594,"uid":204466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c041ee1e82ac92dbbd94b7f43d0b6483ae815250","tid":2022594,"uid":204466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56434a2547b3540cc20366b9970c949047ca7a93","tid":2022594,"uid":204466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e3387d2fa8304cfb429a099167517c97c61ad7","tid":2022594,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:45:00.000Z","msg":"一定要初選，聯署<br />\n先會支持"},{"pid":"b0747c2a3f738139165ce8d8d399d7c225c10f27","tid":2022594,"uid":143343,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:46:18.000Z","msg":"只支持贏初選既人"},{"pid":"2cdf816edacf1a1e62632dca223c823cd6d2dec2","tid":2022594,"uid":56326,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T23:05:11.000Z","msg":"有冇參加初選?<br />\n<br />\n冇就全部票倒落鄒家成/劉穎匡/何桂藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc2ace8d873a60df03b0667cd4c5541904a6d47","tid":